msgstr "Använd teckenstorleken som temat anger"

#: client/options.c:3441 client/options.c:3480
msgid "Disable this to override base font size set by theme by the setting below."
msgstr "Avaktivera detta för att åsidosätta teckensnittets grundstorlek som temat anger med inställningen nedan."

#: client/options.c:3444 client/options.c:3483
msgid "Base Font Size"
msgstr "Grundstorlek för teckensnitt"

#: client/options.c:3445 client/options.c:3484
msgid "Base Font Size. All the fonts' sizes are defined relative to this. This option has effect only if theme font sizes option is disabled."
