#. TRANS: This is help for a server command, so keywords like
#. * "define" in the first column are server keywords that must not
#. * be translated. Do not translate keywords in single quotes, but
#. * strings in <angle brackets> should be translated.
#: common/mapimg.c:693
#, c-format
msgid ""
"This command controls the creation of map images. Supported arguments:\n"
"  define <mapdef>  - define a map image; returns numeric <id>\n"
"  show <id>|all    - list map image definitions or show a specific one\n"
"  create <id>|all  - manually save image(s) for current map state\n"
"  delete <id>|all  - delete map image definition(s)\n"
"  colortest        - create test image(s) showing all colors\n"
"\n"
"Multiple definitions can be active at once. A definition <mapdef> consists of colon-separated options:\n"
"\n"
"option                 (default)  description\n"
"\n"
"format=<[tool|]format> %-10s file format\n"
"show=<show>            %-10s which players to show\n"
"  plrname=<name>                    player name\n"
"  plrid=<id>                        numeric player id\n"
"  plrbv=<bit vector>                see example; first char = id 0\n"
"turns=<turns>          %-10s save image each <turns> turns\n"
"                                  (0=no autosave, save with 'create')\n"
"zoom=<zoom>            %-10s magnification factor (1-5)\n"
"map=<map>              %-10s which map layers to draw\n"
"\n"
"<[tool|]format> = use image format <format>, optionally specifying toolkit <tool>. The following toolkits and formats are compiled in:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"<show> determines which players are represented and how many images are saved by this definition:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"<map> can contain one or more of the following layers:\n"
" - 'a' show area within borders of specified players\n"
" - 'b' show borders of specified players\n"
" - 'c' show cities of specified players\n"
" - 'f' show fog of war (single-player images only)\n"
" - 'k' show only player knowledge (single-player images only)\n"
" - 't' full display of terrain types\n"
" - 'u' show units of specified players\n"
"\n"
"Examples of <mapdef>:\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=tcub:show=all:format=ppm|ppm'\n"
" 'zoom=2:map=tcub:show=each:format=png'\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=tcub:show=plrname:plrname=Otto:format=gif'\n"
" 'zoom=3:map=cu:show=plrbv:plrbv=010011:format=jpg'\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=t:show=none:format=magick|jpg'"
msgstr ""
"Det här kommandot styr skapandet av kartbilder. Argument som stöds:\n"
"  define <kartdefinition>  - definiera en kartbild; returnerar numeriskt <id>\n"
"  show <id>|all    - lista kartbildsdefinitioner eller visa en viss definition\n"
"  create <id>|all  - spara bilder manuellt för kartans aktuella tillstånd\n"
"  delete <id>|all  - ta bort kartbildsdefinitioner\n"
"  colortest        - skapa testbilder som visar alla färger\n"
"\n"
"Flera definitioner kan vara aktiva samtidigt. En definition <kartdefinition> består av kolonseparerade alternativ:\n"
"\n"
"alternativ              (standard)  beskrivning\n"
"\n"
"format=<[verktyg|]format> %-10s filformat\n"
"show=<visning>          %-10s vilka spelare som ska visas\n"
"  plrname=<namn>                    spelarnamn\n"
"  plrid=<id>                        numeriskt spelar-id\n"
"  plrbv=<bitvektor>                 se exemplet; första tecknet = id 0\n"
"turns=<omgångar>        %-10s spara bilden med <omgångar> omgångars mellanrum\n"
"                                  (0=ingen automatisk lagring, spara med 'create')\n"
"zoom=<zoom>             %-10s förstoringsfaktor (1–5)\n"
"map=<karta>             %-10s vilka kartlager som ska ritas\n"
"\n"
"<[verktyg|]format> = använd bildformatet <format> och ange eventuellt bildverktyget <verktyg>. Följande verktyg och format har kompilerats in:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"<visning> avgör vilka spelare som representeras och hur många bilder som sparas av definitionen:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"<karta> kan innehålla ett eller flera av följande lager:\n"
" - 'a' visa området innanför de angivna spelarnas gränser\n"
" - 'b' visa de angivna spelarnas gränser\n"
" - 'c' visa de angivna spelarnas städer\n"
" - 'f' visa krigsdimma (endast bilder för en spelare)\n"
" - 'k' visa endast spelarens kännedom (endast bilder för en spelare)\n"
" - 't' fullständig visning av terrängtyper\n"
" - 'u' visa de angivna spelarnas trupper\n"
"\n"
"Exempel på <kartdefinition>:\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=tcub:show=all:format=ppm|ppm'\n"
" 'zoom=2:map=tcub:show=each:format=png'\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=tcub:show=plrname:plrname=Otto:format=gif'\n"
" 'zoom=3:map=cu:show=plrbv:plrbv=010011:format=jpg'\n"
" 'zoom=1:map=t:show=none:format=magick|jpg'"

