#: data/civ2/terrain.ruleset:1596 data/classic/terrain.ruleset:1899 data/sandbox/terrain.ruleset:2225 data/civ2civ3/terrain.ruleset:2115 data/multiplayer/terrain.ruleset:1871
msgid "Ivory"
